<h2 class="text-center">{l s='"Calculator" tab' mod='cdek20'}</h2>
<hr>

<strong>{l s='Field "Delay Departure"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='You can increase the delivery time by the selected value.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='From the drop-down list, select the required number of additional days' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='When choosing a delivery, the user will see the delivery time, taking into account additional days.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br></br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Estimated Departure Time"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Specify the time at which you will expect the courier.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Required for door-to-door deliveries' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Courier Waiting Delay" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Allows you to shift the date to the expectation of the courier. Values in days.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Example: if you sent a request for delivery to CDEK today, but are ready to hand over the goods to the courier only tomorrow or the next day, then select the required value in the settings.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Courier start time" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='During the day, from what time will you wait for the courier to transfer the goods.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Specify the required time, but not earlier than 09.00 am' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Courier end time" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='During the day, until what time will you wait for the courier to transfer the goods.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Specify the required time, but no later than 22.00 pm' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Commission / Discount for delivery"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='You can add a commission / discount to shipping' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='If you enter a numerical value, then there will be a commission' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='If you enter a numeric value with a minus sign, then there will be a discount' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='You can enter the value as an amount or a percentage' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Decrease in declared value by %" ' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Reduces the declared value of goods by the specified percentage.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Insurance depends on the declared value of the goods.' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Insurance is calculated only in LC SDEK' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='Enter values: 0-100 100 - disables insurance' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
<strong>{l s='Field "Impact on delivery from cart amount"' mod='cdek20'}</strong></br>
{l s='Increase / decrease in shipping costs as a percentage of the cart amount' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='If you enter a numerical value, then there will be a commission' mod='cdek20'}</br>
{l s='If you enter a numeric value with a minus sign, then there will be a discount' mod='cdek20'}</br>
</br>
